name: ads-power-clone-vue
description: A Vue 3 clone of AdsPower fingerprint browser management software

scripts.start: npm run build && ELECTRON_DISABLE_SECURITY_WARNINGS=true ELECTRON_NO_ATTACH_CONSOLE=true ELECTRON_ENABLE_LOGGING=false ELECTRON_ENABLE_SECURE_RESTORABLE_STATE=true ELECTRON_ENABLE_NATIVE_IMAGE_WARNINGS=false ELECTRON_DISABLE_GPU_SANDBOX=true ELECTRON_NO_SANDBOX=true electron .
scripts.dev: npm run build && ELECTRON_DISABLE_SECURITY_WARNINGS=true ELECTRON_NO_ATTACH_CONSOLE=true ELECTRON_ENABLE_LOGGING=false ELECTRON_ENABLE_SECURE_RESTORABLE_STATE=true ELECTRON_ENABLE_NATIVE_IMAGE_WARNINGS=false ELECTRON_DISABLE_GPU_SANDBOX=true ELECTRON_NO_SANDBOX=true electron . --dev
